{"about_the_game":"<strong>In the Wild</strong> is an educational game where you control animals, explore environments, complete tasks, and play mini-games.<br><br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575380/extras/Screenshot_668_50.png?t=1635836472\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Educational</h2>Learn interesting facts about every animal you can control! <br>Our in-game guide will teach you different facts about each animal as you use them.<br>Collect each fact you discover in your book for future reference. Collect all facts and earn a trophy for that animal!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Entertaining</h2>Take control of each animal and run around, play games, complete quests, and unlock items!<br> With tons of animal-specific mini-games, there's always something to do around the world.<br> Explore and find new islands with new animals, containing unique content with each location.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Day and Night, Rain and Snow</h2>Our dynamic time and weather system enables an additional layer of interaction with the world. The time of day and weather determines the available mini-games, quests, and unlockables. As a player, you can choose to use real-world time (relative to their time-zone) or a customizable in-game time. You also have the ability to enable and disable different weather types. How you play is completely up to you. <br> <br><br>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575380/extras/Screenshot_669_50.png?t=1635836472\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Wolf","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1575380/fda7e2a5de9b12b249455e3df636a5c21b20a87e.jpg"},{"name":"The Bear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1575380/9a1b30b709ecd1af8181f9e2fc631def1e630468.